data.description: Stop the Car!! You will fall in love this all brick spacious 1757 sq ft ranch home as soon as you walk through the front door! The large living room has beautiful windows to look out on your covered front porch! The additional family room has a beautiful fire place and is very cozy! The extra large eat in kitchen would be great for any gathering! It has a regular stove and a built in cook top and oven! The kitchen has updated has a ton of cabinets and is very open.. All kitchen appliances remain with the home. This home also has 3 large bedrooms and 1 full bath and 2 1/2 baths. Lots of windows to look out at your .66 private acre lot! This home has a new water heater, and very well insulated. Very dry crawl space.. The back yard has a fire pit, and a gazebo. Large 2 car garage attached and a half car garage/shed.. you can also spend your evening playing basketball on your poured concrete basketball court! sq ft is approximate if critical buyers should verify.
